{"tid":1915451,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"［又嚟老撚土問題］等錶位","createTime":"2020-03-08T08:11:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-09T12:01:49.000Z","uid":13495,"like":63,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"5b12d29c62e3c50f20c65cb20da687f526205c48","tid":1915451,"uid":13495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T08:11:28.000Z","msg":"話說今日去撚左南區 去到錶位入口有架車停左喺度唔撚郁又唔打死火燈 咁咪咇鳩佢一下叫佢郁一郁俾我入去等<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n 點知個呀叔同我講話呢度係一架出一架入咁等<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（當時係爆場）咁我架車就俾佢block撚住左喺出面條單線路度 搞到後面要慢車過<br />\n<br />\n 跟住好彩開始塞車嗰陣有三架車一齊走先冇塞 泊完之後我過佢屌個呀叔老母問鳩佢係咪第一日等錶位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢咁撚樣等法出面成條路就咁俾撚左佢啦<br />\n<br />\n講真揸咁耐車 每次去錶位等都係你停喺嗰幾架就等嗰幾架㗎啦 如果好似佢咁講一出一入咁同就直接等私家停車場啦屌你<br />\n<br />\n咁究撚竟係邊個先啱？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 停喺嗰幾架就等嗰幾架<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不嬲都係一出一入㗎啦屌你"},{"pid":"b1d612ddf3b560541bfc1e53d69affa44c7b2341","tid":1915451,"uid":62020,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T08:14:20.000Z","msg":"邊個惡邊個話事, 呢D野應該先到先得既<br />\n不過只係怕人地搞你部車, 買部平嫁啦<br />\n<br />\n唔通隻眼望到就係自己既咩"},{"pid":"ea41ca768f7e4f0f27a8da12d54adb89b6f29e85","tid":1915451,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T08:21:05.000Z","msg":"理撚得佢<br />\n不嬲都係喺錶位場入面等<br />\n呢啲嘢自己自律啦<br />\n佢唔死入去就落車拍佢片<br />\n阻街刑事 叫佢洗定8月15"},{"pid":"096bad90c2bf39a2ba865ca680305074ac902c23","tid":1915451,"uid":51105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T08:21:20.000Z","msg":"佢都on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />冇其他人去屌佢就更on9"},{"pid":"c0f877d910de0a2aa7e02c6809c42ca495a47436","tid":1915451,"uid":13495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea41ca768f7e4f0f27a8da12d54adb89b6f29e85","tid":1915451,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T08:21:05.000Z","msg":"理撚得佢<br />\n不嬲都係喺錶位場入面等<br />\n呢啲嘢自己自律啦<br />\n佢唔死入去就落車拍佢片<br />\n阻街刑事 叫佢洗定8月15"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T08:23:21.000Z","msg":"其實開始塞嗰一刻我係諗住揸前喺出口倒車入理鳩佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點知咁啱有三架車走"},{"pid":"38c1d6eda3fe7b435b7aa4f8e0ff76d49860f873","tid":1915451,"uid":120955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T09:04:06.000Z","msg":"一啲啲 度度唔同㗎喎<br />\n赤柱嗰個係咁"},{"pid":"7e7f7f7c744ca1f2e43c19161b568ff92f466713","tid":1915451,"uid":201640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T09:10:49.000Z","msg":"搭單問，之前有次等錶位，泊後一個車位架車走，我就打左燈諗住等佢走就泊，點撚知後幾個車位個呀叔篤上黎泊，佢話等左好耐我就到左冇幾耐，咁但係正路唔係我等個幾個位就係我泊架啦咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63616f5c82a6b2a116f663d3462094d9a4b0160a","tid":1915451,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7e7f7f7c744ca1f2e43c19161b568ff92f466713","tid":1915451,"uid":201640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T09:10:49.000Z","msg":"搭單問，之前有次等錶位，泊後一個車位架車走，我就打左燈諗住等佢走就泊，點撚知後幾個車位個呀叔篤上黎泊，佢話等左好耐我就到左冇幾耐，咁但係正路唔係我等個幾個位就係我泊架啦咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T09:12:43.000Z","msg":"咩等咗好耐<br />\n冇人見到佢<br />\n屌柒佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c5ac06a49c466152c124cdb6576f6eb3efec3d1","tid":1915451,"uid":201640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"63616f5c82a6b2a116f663d3462094d9a4b0160a","tid":1915451,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7e7f7f7c744ca1f2e43c19161b568ff92f466713","tid":1915451,"uid":201640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T09:10:49.000Z","msg":"搭單問，之前有次等錶位，泊後一個車位架車走，我就打左燈諗住等佢走就泊，點撚知後幾個車位個呀叔篤上黎泊，佢話等左好耐我就到左冇幾耐，咁但係正路唔係我等個幾個位就係我泊架啦咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T09:12:43.000Z","msg":"咩等咗好耐<br />\n冇人見到佢<br />\n屌柒佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T09:13:49.000Z","msg":"我有落車屌佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但佢大條道理咁唔讓"},{"pid":"7cf56ff3b529834e7cc6cbc5ecab1840ccdb88e0","tid":1915451,"uid":51105,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0c5ac06a49c466152c124cdb6576f6eb3efec3d1","tid":1915451,"uid":201640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"63616f5c82a6b2a116f663d3462094d9a4b0160a","tid":1915451,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7e7f7f7c744ca1f2e43c19161b568ff92f466713","tid":1915451,"uid":201640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T09:10:49.000Z","msg":"搭單問，之前有次等錶位，泊後一個車位架車走，我就打左燈諗住等佢走就泊，點撚知後幾個車位個呀叔篤上黎泊，佢話等左好耐我就到左冇幾耐，咁但係正路唔係我等個幾個位就係我泊架啦咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T09:12:43.000Z","msg":"咩等咗好耐<br />\n冇人見到佢<br />\n屌柒佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T09:13:49.000Z","msg":"我有落車屌佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但佢大條道理咁唔讓"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T09:18:25.000Z","msg":"你唔係揸靚車嘅話咪去同佢鬥頂囉"},{"pid":"8e1da390b596d7381829b5fc1cb0063d2c9cb347","tid":1915451,"uid":218411,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T09:36:53.000Z","msg":"睇情況嘅啫<br />\n好似呢度咁一定要一出一入㗎喎<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SN7QZe9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSN7QZe9.png&h=cfe388c8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4d99836f6f46e52bcbc71a35914e75d9f80db508","tid":1915451,"uid":233593,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T09:39:58.000Z","msg":"聽落似係赤柱個場，入面有黃柱藍柱，<br />\n有時黃柱有吉位但係排頭果個等藍柱，<br />\n所以我都唔係幾同意呢個排隊法，<br />\n但係去過幾次都聽到啲廢老話係咁排"},{"pid":"f7ab6ea7c64bdb651a2b6e0f43be3cb6e7f45b2c","tid":1915451,"uid":66365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e1da3