plyTime":"2020-03-08T13:55:52.000Z","msg":"分享少少經驗<br />\n呢種情況我會選擇入後波先(如果係睇到/溝通咗佢係想走既話)<br />\n有4個車位應該夠<br />\n佢架車喺你車頭走係最好 預位預得好過睇鏡<br />\n防守性又會強少少<br />\n等架車走咗先向後行會慢過人地向前頂住你<br />\n成件事會比較被動"},{"pid":"d51450516c54f5c1d12024553dba62423e1eebb4","tid":1915451,"uid":13495,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T06:01:54.000Z","msg":"屌老母又遇到個傻既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />街頭等街尾 隔十個車位走過嚟同我講佢嚟先"},{"pid":"fb52ae65314c5bb6304ba83fa256dd07b8c0ac89","tid":1915451,"uid":201640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d51450516c54f5c1d12024553dba62423e1eebb4","tid":1915451,"uid":13495,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T06:01:54.000Z","msg":"屌老母又遇到個傻既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />街頭等街尾 隔十個車位走過嚟同我講佢嚟先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T06:40:07.000Z","msg":"同佢鬥傻話琴晚開始等緊啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a58efe3bb3e0137955b3159df8f6a5cde12403b","tid":1915451,"uid":6316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e1da390b596d7381829b5fc1cb0063d2c9cb347","tid":1915451,"uid":218411,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T09:36:53.000Z","msg":"睇情況嘅啫<br />\n好似呢度咁一定要一出一入㗎喎<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SN7QZe9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSN7QZe9.png&h=cfe388c8&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T06:48:59.000Z","msg":"真係睇邊個場, 呢個場一定係一出一入, 如果唔係會定死晒+ 你可能好耐都冇位, 一出一入係方便大家同有效率<br />\n<br />\n但有 d 場係唔得既"},{"pid":"b1baa14a60ccf12fc3754e231ba1686e4c5f1ee6","tid":1915451,"uid":23897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d51450516c54f5c1d12024553dba62423e1eebb4","tid":1915451,"uid":13495,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T06:01:54.000Z","msg":"屌老母又遇到個傻既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />街頭等街尾 隔十個車位走過嚟同我講佢嚟先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T06:54:15.000Z","msg":"<a h